{"tid":271404,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【恒地股東會】夠鐘開會 過百股東排隊未入得場","createTime":"2017-06-05T05:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T07:30:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4250790b6bc829193d87a27484c0a50f82f53957","tid":271404,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170605/large/1496636311_9c3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170605%2Flarge%2F1496636311_9c3b.jpg&h=72c8d02b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170605/large/1496636313_5787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170605%2Flarge%2F1496636313_5787.jpg&h=37e2b2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒基系今早舉行股東大會，原訂11時半召開的恒地（012）股東會，至開場時間仍有逾百名小股東在會場外排隊登記，有部份人先參加恒基發展（097）股東會，完場後已取得禮物包，再度排隊進場。有小股東投訴「今年特別耐、特別多人」，指應加開登記櫃枱應付，「夠哂鐘，不如唔好開啦。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃翹恩"},{"pid":"43b1c920cd370748f27914dd812633620c46ec85","tid":271404,"uid":34621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"人很多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}